      <p>Most treatments you've probably tried focus on managing symptoms, not fixing the cause:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Pads and liners:</strong> They catch leaks but don't stop them. You're still living in fear.</li>
        <li><strong>Pelvic floor exercises:</strong> Helpful, but incomplete. Without the right minerals, your muscles can't fully recover.</li>
        <li><strong>Prescription medications:</strong> Often cause side effects like dry mouth, constipation, or dizziness. And they're expensive.</li>
        <li><strong>Surgical procedures:</strong> Invasive, costly, and not always effective. Plus, recovery time can be months.</li>
